</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation id="131C6095991DFFA2FF4F572E6300E922" box="[241,269,870,894]" captionStart="FIGURES 10 – 18" captionStartId="5.[151,264,1877,1900]" captionTargetBox="[189,1407,194,1798]" captionTargetId="figure@5.[151,1436,193,1856]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="FIGURES 10 – 18. Genitalia and sternite. 10 – 14. male genitalia. 10, Micardia pulcherrima (Noct- 00275); 11, M. pulcherrima (Noct- 00273); 12, M. pallens sp. nov. (Noct- 00271); 13, M. distincta sp. nov. (Noct- 00272); 14, M. minuta sp. nov. (Noct- 00274). 15 – 16. female genitalia. 15, M. pallens sp. nov. (Noct- 00277); 16, M. munda (Noct- 00276). 17 – 18. eighth abdominal sternite of female. 17, M. pallens sp. nov. (Noct- 00277); 18, M. munda (Noct- 00276). Scales: 1 mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/281961/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="49">14</figureCitation>
